room_title: Escape room "Rampancy" by Denver Escape Room in Denver
room_address: 11674 N Huron St, Suite 300 Northglenn, CO 80234
room_description: Exploring the abandoned remains of a testing and enrichment facility you stumble upon a construct long forgotten. A rogue artificial intelligence named Kel, who locks you into a chamber and forces you to participate in his experiments. Can you shutdown the system and escape his grasp?
